label: Union Jack
title: Union_Jack_(American_newspaper)
exrest: The Union Jack was the only monthly newspaper featuring news from the United Kingdom, produced and published in the United States. The publication is aimed at British expatriates in the United States. It was established in 1982 and is distributed in every state. The paper ceased publication in July 2016.
